# Steps
1. Scope: identify what infrastrucute you need (requirements)
2. Authoe: Write code that defines infrastructure
3. Intialize: Install any necessary plugin/ pre requirsites
Plan: Preview changes before implementing

#Type of code
Terraform is declarative, not procedural! This means anything written with Terraform is what you want the end result of the configuration to be.
Terraform providers will automatically create or destrory resources in the correct order there is no need to wirte terraform code sequentially.
